Works. Execution like so:

markup 3 "Fundamental Theorem of Calculus"

markup: the executable
3: the maximum depth of links to explore. 0 retrieves just the specified page; 1 retrieves all of the pages it links to, and so on.
"Fundamental Theorem of Calculus": the page on which to begin exploration. Must be a valid ProofWiki page title. Must be in quotes. Recommended to copy/paste.
